room_title: Escape room "The Zombie Kitchen" by TeamEscape 262 in Milwaukee
room_address: N80W14942 Appleton Avenue, Menomonee Falls, WI 53051
room_description: In this new world, Zombies are commonplace and they have their own restaurants. The best in town is the Zombie Kitchen. Our Chef Tony "the walker" Rotini is MIA. Perhaps he was the latest main course. Your job is to put together today's special and present it to our esteemed food critic Jonny "Bones" Jones before time runs out. Failure means the next special will be you.
